trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartitionCollection" /> class is a read-only collection that contains <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartitionCollection" /> 类是一个包含 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> 对象的只读集合。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> object to search for in this collection.
trans-unit.target: 要在此集合中搜索的 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> 对象。

trans-unit.source: Determines if the specified <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> object is in this collection.
trans-unit.target: 确定指定 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> 对象是否在此集合中。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> is in this collection, otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> 在此集合中，则为 <see langword="true" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="applicationPartition" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="applicationPartition" /> 为 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: The array of <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> objects that receives the elements of this collection.
trans-unit.target: 接收此集合元素的 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> 对象的数组。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index in <c>applicationPartitions</c> where this method starts copying this collection.
trans-unit.target: 在 <c>applicationPartitions</c> 中从零开始的索引，此方法从该位置开始复制此集合。

trans-unit.source: Copies all <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> objects in this collection to the specified array, starting at the specified index of the target array.
trans-unit.target: 将此集合中的所有 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> 对象复制指定的数组，从目标数组的指定索引处开始。

trans-unit.source: A call to the underlying directory service resulted in an error.
trans-unit.target: 对基础目录服务的调用导致了错误。

trans-unit.source: The destination array is not large enough, based on the source collection size and the <paramref name="index" /> specified.
trans-unit.target: 对于源集合的大小和指定的 <paramref name="index" /> 而言，目标数组不够大。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="applicationPartitions" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="applicationPartitions" /> 为 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="index" /> specified is out of range of the destination array.
trans-unit.target: 指定的 <paramref name="index" /> 超出了目标数组的范围。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> object to search for in this collection.
trans-unit.target: 要在此集合中搜索的 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> 对象。

trans-unit.source: Returns the first occurrence of the specified <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> object in this collection.
trans-unit.target: 返回在此集合中指定的 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> 对象的第一个匹配项。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the first matching item.
trans-unit.target: 第一个匹配项的从零开始的索引。

trans-unit.source: -1 if no member of this collection is identical to <paramref name="applicationPartition" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果此集合中不存在与 <paramref name="applicationPartition" /> 相同的成员，则为 -1。

trans-unit.source: A call to the underlying directory service resulted in an error.
trans-unit.target: 对基础目录服务的调用导致了错误。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="applicationPartition" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="applicationPartition" /> 为 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> object to get.
trans-unit.target: 要获取的 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> 对象的从零开始的索引。

trans-unit.source: Gets an <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> object in this collection.
trans-unit.target: 获取此集合中的 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> 对象。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> object that exists at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: 位于指定索引位置的 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> 对象。

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="index" /> specified is out of range of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 指定的 <paramref name="index" /> 超出了集合的范围。
